Set Choice `RequestChoice "'Capital Punishment' (preview V3.0) HD Starter" "How many games do you want to play?" "Only one, please" "Wanna play till the death!" "None, I hate violence"`
If Val $Choice EQ 2  
 Mount SmallRAD
 MakeDir SmallRad:S
 Echo `cd`/capitalpunishment.v3 > SmallRad:S/StartUp-Sequence
 Reboot
EndIf
If Val $Choice EQ 1
 Capitalpunishment.v3
 RequestChoice "" "Warning! System will be restarted." "Okay, I already saved my high score." > NIL:
EndIf
If Val $Choice EQ 0
 RequestChoice "" "Lamer!" "I am so STUPID" > NIL:
EndIf
